রাসূলের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/048_013_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14870,"position":6,"arabic":"فَإِنَّآ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই সেক্ষেত্রে আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/048_013_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14871,"position":7,"arabic":"أَعْتَدْنَا","translation":"আমরা প্রস্তুত করে রেখেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/048_013_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14872,"position":8,"arabic":"لِلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","translation":"কাফেরদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/048_013_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14873,"position":9,"arabic":"سَعِيرًۭا","translation":"জ্বলন্ত আগুন","audioUrl":"wbw/048_013_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":14874,"position":10,"arabic":"١٣","translation":"(১৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":14,"arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ مُلْكُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ يَغْفِرُ لِمَن يَشَآءُ وَيُعَذِّبُ مَن يَشَآءُ ۚ وَكَانَ ٱللَّهُ غَفُورًۭا رَّحِيمًۭا","translation":"But God’s is the dominion over the heavens and the earth: He forgives whomever He wills, and imposes suffering on whomever He wills - and [withal,] He is indeed much-forgiving, a dispenser of grace.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4597.mp3","surahId":48,"words":[{"id":15929,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহরই জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15930,"position":2,"arabic":"مُلْكُ","translation":"সার্বভৌমত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15931,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশের","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15932,"position":4,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ","translation":"ও পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15934,"position":5,"arabic":"يَغْفِرُ","translation":"তিনি মাফ করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15935,"position":6,"arabic":"لِمَن","translation":"যাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15936,"position":7,"arabic":"يَشَآءُ","translation":"তিনি ইচ্ছে করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15937,"position":8,"arabic":"وَيُعَذِّبُ","translation":"ও তিনি শাস্তি দেন","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15938,"position":9,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"যাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15939,"position":10,"arabic":"يَشَآءُ ۚ","translation":"তিনি ইচ্ছে করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15941,"position":11,"arabic":"وَكَانَ","translation":"আর হলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15942,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15943,"position":13,"arabic":"غَفُورًۭا","translation":"ক্ষমাশীল","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15944,"position":14,"arabic":"رَّحِيمًۭا","translation":"দয়ালু","audioUrl":"wbw/048_014_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":15945,"position":15,"arabic":"١٤","translation":"(১৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":15,"arabic":"سَيَقُولُ ٱلْمُخَلَّفُونَ إِذَا ٱنطَلَقْتُمْ إِلَىٰ مَغَانِمَ لِتَأْخُذُوهَا ذَرُونَا نَتَّبِعْكُمْ ۖ يُرِيدُونَ أَن يُبَدِّلُوا۟ كَلَٰمَ ٱللَّهِ ۚ قُل لَّن تَتَّبِعُونَا كَذَٰلِكُمْ قَالَ ٱللَّهُ مِن قَبْلُ ۖ فَسَيَقُولُونَ بَلْ تَحْسُدُونَنَا ۚ بَلْ كَانُوا۟ لَا يَفْقَهُونَ إِلَّا قَلِيلًۭا","translation":"As soon as you [O believers] are about to set forth on a war that promises booty, those who stayed behind [aforetime] will surely say, “Allow us to go with you” - [thus showing that] they would like to alter the Word of God. Say: “By no means shall you go with us: God has declared aforetime [to whom all spoils shall belong].” Thereupon they will [surely] answer, “Nay, but you begrudge us [our share of booty]!” Nay, they can grasp but so little of the truth!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4598.mp3","surahId":48,"words":[{"id":17157